{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8d7d91ab4f","title":"对罗瑞卿关于一起杀人案的判处意见的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"97bedba54a","index":0,"year":1952,"month":10,"day":6,"articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"}],"tags":[{"id":"6c3c62f283","name":"罗瑞卿","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"2dab336c7d","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"王剑朋，曾任广州市人民政府企业管理局局长，三反运动中，因被揭发有贪污问题而受到监管。监管期间，他有计划地揽死监管他的警卫人员，并杀死检举他的人。广州市人民法院决定判处他死刑，立即执行。广州市公安局和人民检察署对此提出异议，主张判处死刑缓期执行。后经中央公安部和最高人民检察署复议，决定维持原判，立即执行。"}],"contents":[{"id":"20166d8c45","type":"title","text":"对罗瑞卿\"关于一起杀人案的判处意见的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"},{"id":"2dab336c7d","type":"paragraph","text":"周邓阅，退罗瑞卿同志，并请罗转告蓝副检查（察）长以，同意他维持原判，对王剑朋处以极刑立即执行","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"},{"id":"6085abbf97","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"},{"id":"ac4e0ec8e4","type":"paragraph","text":"十月六日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"},{"id":"708f936a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"T1罗瑞卿，当时任中央人民政府公安部部长。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"},{"id":"31c058e9d0","type":"paragraph","text":"周，指周恩来。邓，指邓小平，当时任政务院副总理。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"},{"id":"dfea4c2236","type":"paragraph","text":"指中央人民政府最高人民检察署副检察长蓝公武","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d91ab4f"}],"page":{"id":"c0b3e22a9e","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"8d7d